"title": "2345: Jesus Christ, kingdom of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2345",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The present and future realm in which Jesus Christ exercises full authority, and through which he triumphs over all opposition.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's kingdom is a heavenly kingdom</h2>\n<h3>It is not of this world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:36\">JHN 18:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:6\">REV 5:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:10\">REV 7:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1\">REV 21:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:3\">REV 21:3</a></p>\n<h3>The kingdom was given to him by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:14\">DAN 7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:1\">PSA 72:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:44\">DAN 2:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18\">MAT 28:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:15\">JHN 16:15</a></p>\n<h3>The kingdom is his by right</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15-Col1:16\">COL 1:15–1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:8\">HEB 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:6\">PSA 45:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:13\">REV 22:13</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ inherits the kingdom promised to David</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:32\">LUK 1:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:12\">ROM 15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:10\">ISA 11:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:27\">REV 2:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:9\">PSA 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ reveals God's kingdom on earth</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ brought in God's kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:17\">MAT 4:17</a></strong> <em>The expressions “kingdom of heaven” and the “kingdom of God” are interchangeable.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:2\">MAT 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:7\">MAT 10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:28\">MAT 12:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:20\">LUK 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:20-Luke17:21\">LUK 17:20–17:21</a></p>\n<h3>Miracles are a sign of the kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:14-John6:15\">JHN 6:14–6:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26-Matt8:27\">MAT 8:26–8:27</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:39-Mark4:41\">MRK 4:39–4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:24-Luke8:25\">LUK 8:24–8:25</a> <em>authority over the created world</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:2-Matt11:5\">MAT 11:2–11:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:19-Luke7:22\">LUK 7:19–7:22</a> <em>authority to heal</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:11-Luke7:15\">LUK 7:11–7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:17-Rev1:18\">REV 1:17–1:18</a></p>\n<h3>Parables are a sign of the kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:1-Matt13:52\">MAT 13:1–13:52</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:1-Mark4:34\">MRK 4:1–4:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:4-Luke8:15\">LUK 8:4–8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:18-Luke13:21\">LUK 13:18–13:21</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ exercises kingdom authority today</h2>\n<h3>Believers enter Jesus Christ's kingdom immediately</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:42-Luke23:43\">LUK 23:42–23:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:3\">MAT 5:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:20\">LUK 6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:11\">MAT 11:11</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are redeemed from the kingdom of darkness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:12-Col1:13\">COL 1:12–1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:5\">EPH 5:5</a></p>\n<h3>Believers enjoy the blessings of Jesus Christ's kingdom now</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:19\">MAT 16:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:22\">DAN 7:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:27\">DAN 7:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:32\">LUK 12:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:29-Luke22:30\">LUK 22:29–22:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:5\">JAS 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:5-Rev1:6\">REV 1:5–1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:9\">REV 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:21\">REV 3:21</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ rules over every authority now</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:22\">1PE 3:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:20-Eph1:23\">EPH 1:20–1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:9\">PHP 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:10\">COL 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2\">HEB 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:10\">REV 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:16\">REV 19:16</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's kingdom will be fully established at his return</h2>\n<h3>His kingdom will come with power at a specific moment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31\">MAT 25:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:10\">ZEC 9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30-Matt24:31\">MAT 24:30–24:31</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26-Mark13:27\">MRK 13:26–13:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:27\">LUK 21:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:1\">2TI 4:1</a></p>\n<h3>His kingdom will replace all earthly authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:15\">REV 11:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:24-1Cor15:25\">1CO 15:24–15:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:50-1Cor15:52\">1CO 15:50–15:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:20-Phil3:21\">PHP 3:20–3:21</a></p>\n<h3>All creation will acknowledge Jesus Christ's kingship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:10-Phil2:11\">PHP 2:10–2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:6-Ps2:8\">PSA 2:6–2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:13\">REV 5:13</a></p>\n<h3>His kingdom lasts for ever</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:33\">LUK 1:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:7\">ISA 9:7</a></p>",
